  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. When Alice trains, it&rsquo;s recommended that <span class=\"italic\">p</span> be between 0.5 and 0.85. Therefore, her target training heart rate is represented by the values of <span class=\"italic\">H</span> corresponding to <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"0 point 5 is less than or equal to p, which is less than or equal to 0 point 8 5\"></span>. When <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"p equals 0 point 5\"></span>, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"H equals, 120 times 0 point 5, plus 60\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"H equals 120\"></span>. When <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"p equals 0 point 8 5\"></span>, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"H equals, 120 times 0 point 8 5, plus, 60\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"H equals 162\"></span>. Therefore, the inequality that describes Alice&rsquo;s target training heart rate is <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"120 is less than or equal to H, which is less than or equal to 162\"></span>.<p>Choice B is incorrect. This inequality describes Alice&rsquo;s target heart rate for <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"0 point 3 5 is less than or equal to p, which is less than or equal to 0 point 5\"></span>. Choice C is incorrect. This inequality describes her target heart rate for <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"0 is less than or equal to p, which is less than or equal to 0 point 8 5\"></span>. Choice D is incorrect. This inequality describes&nbsp; her target heart rate for <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"0 is less than or equal to p, which is less than or equal to 0 point 3 5\"></span>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>\n",
